query:
INSERT INTO profiles (short_id, owner_id, name, community, mods, code)
        VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5, $6)
        ON CONFLICT(short_id)
        DO UPDATE SET
            name = EXCLUDED.name,
            mods = EXCLUDED.mods,
            code = EXCLUDED.code,
            updated_at = NOW()
        RETURNING
            short_id AS "short_id: ProfileId", 
            created_at,
            updated_at
